"Arguments *file*, *protocol*, *fix_imports* and *buffer_callback* have the "
"same meaning as in the :class:`Pickler` constructor."
msgstr ""
"引數 *file*、*protocol*、*fix_imports* 和 *buffer_callback* 的意義與 :class:"
