"有 :attr:`~object.__dict__` 實例、但沒有 :attr:`~object.__slots__` 實例的類"
"別，其預設狀態為 ``self.__dict__``。"

#: ../../library/pickle.rst:631
msgid ""
"For a class that has an instance :attr:`~object.__dict__` and :attr:`~object."
