"__reduce__`）、也可以回傳 :data:`NotImplemented` 以回退至原始的行為。"

#: ../../library/pickle.rst:910
msgid ""
"If both the :attr:`~Pickler.dispatch_table` and :meth:`~Pickler."
"reducer_override` are defined, then :meth:`~Pickler.reducer_override` method "
